org.conqat.engine.service.shared.client

Enum EServiceApiVersion

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.lang.Enum<EServiceApiVersion>
      • org.conqat.engine.service.shared.client.EServiceApiVersion
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable, java.lang.Comparable<EServiceApiVersion>
    Deprecated. 
    Use @PublicApi to version new api endpoints, which uses a versioning scheme that matches the Teamscale version.

    public enum EServiceApiVersion
extends java.lang.Enum<EServiceApiVersion>
    The version of the service API as used by the service clients. In case of compatible extensions to the API, we increase CURRENT_VERSION, thus old clients can still talk to this server. For breaking changes we set both CURRENT_VERSION and MIN_SUPPORTED_VERSION to the value of ( CURRENT_VERSION + 1).
